WEBVTT

00:11.800 --> 00:14.685
<i>And here they are,</i>
<i>the Sofa Speedsters--</i>

00:14.719 --> 00:17.554
<i>the Simpsons</i>
<i>on Brown Lightning!</i>

00:17.589 --> 00:19.189
<i>The Piggly Wiggums!</i>

00:19.224 --> 00:20.691
<i>The Bumble Buggy!</i>

00:20.725 --> 00:22.059
<i>The Greed Hornet!</i>

00:22.093 --> 00:23.410
<i>Dr. Groom!</i>

00:23.445 --> 00:25.029
<i>Glasgow-A-Go-Go!</i>

00:25.063 --> 00:26.563
<i>Hick Dastardly...</i>

00:26.598 --> 00:28.232
<i>and the Franken-continental!</i>

00:28.266 --> 00:31.552
<i>We'll be sitting pretty</i>
<i>at the finish line!</i>

